        {
            "title": "地產｜柏傲莊III折實均價2.1萬 二手折讓10%  設四房提名優惠",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"地產｜柏傲莊III折實均價2.1萬 二手折讓10% 設四房提名優惠\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">地產｜柏傲莊III折實均價2.1萬 二手折讓10% 設四房提名優惠</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">新世界發展(00017)旗下大圍柏傲莊III今日(9日)更新價單。項目最新上載1A號價單，當中50伙修訂售價，該批單位中，若採用120天現金優惠付款計劃，扣除最高折扣20%計算，折實售價由745.8萬起，折實呎價由19597元起。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">當中，價單1A 號包括11伙一房戶、25伙兩房戶及14伙三房戶，實用面積310至814平方呎，以定價計總值約7.21億。價單定價932.3萬至2210.4萬元，價單呎價介乎24498至32261元。折實售價745.8萬至1768.3萬元，折實呎價介乎19597至25806元，折實平均呎價21344元。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-4c95eef6-a49e-3889-bcbe-99c61e40b632-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">價單最低售價單位為第8座(8A)12樓E室，一房間隔，實用面積310平方呎，定價932.3萬，呎價30074元，折實售價745.8萬，折實呎價24058元。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">是次特設「尊貴業主提名優惠」，於招標時購買四房一套大宅，可以提名一位指定親屬，而於招標時購買四房雙套大宅，可以提名兩位指定親屬，被提名人於價單購買單位時，可享額外1%折扣優惠。是次推出的內園單位是三期之中景觀最優越，與一期及二期相比，享有最廣闊的景致。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2-%E6%9F%8F%E5%82%B2%E8%8E%8Aiii%E6%8A%98%E5%AF%A6%E5%9D%87%E5%83%B92-1%E8%90%AC-%E4%BA%8C%E6%89%8B%E6%8A%98%E8%AE%9310-%E8%A8%AD%E5%9B%9B%E6%88%BF%E6%8F%90%E5%90%8D%E5%84%AA%E6%83%A0-093509867.html",
