        {
            "title": "荃灣富華中心吉舖丟空兩年終租出 飲食集團20萬月租承接　較高峰期36.8萬跌46%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/YsBPVzqDdJCJNSV.UB_FEA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/958805f03a594635e3177a00f435784e\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure></div>",
